    label "articulo::5::BIOMX-DB: A web application for the BIOFACQUIM natural product database"
    tipo "articulo"
    nombre "BIOMX-DB: A web application for the BIOFACQUIM natural product database"
    indice "5"
    Year "2024"
    ISBN ""
    ISSN "1868-1743"
    Doi "10.1002/minf.202400060"
    URL "https://www.scopus.com/pages/publications/85195311095?origin=resultslist"
    Area "ISBD"
    Abstract "Natural product databases are an integral part of chemoinformatics and computer-aided drug design. Despite their pivotal role, a distinct scarcity of projects in Latin America, particularly in Mexico, provides accessible tools of this nature. Herein, we introduce BIOMX-DB, an open and freely accessible web-based database designed to address this gap. BIOMX-DB enhances the features of the existing Mexican natural product database, BIOFACQUIM, by incorporating advanced search, filtering, and download capabilities. The user-friendly interface of BIOMX-DB aims to provide an intuitive experience for researchers."
  ]
