    label "articulo::232::Ortho-Unit Polygons can be Guarded with at most n-48 Guards"
    tipo "articulo"
    nombre "Ortho-Unit Polygons can be Guarded with at most n-48 Guards"
    indice "232"
    Year "2025"
    ISBN ""
    ISSN "0911-0119"
    Doi "10.1007/s00373-024-02880-8"
    URL "https://www.scopus.com/pages/publications/85213541727?origin=resultslist"
    Area "TC"
    Abstract "An orthogonal polygon is called an ortho-unit polygon if its vertices have integer coordinates, and all of its edges have length one. In this paper we prove that any ortho-unit polygon with n &#8805; 12 vertices can be guarded with at most &#8970; n - 4 8 &#8971; guards, which is a tight bound."
  ]
